headline: Bernstein says market overreacting to Trump order, sees limited new impact on PBMs
summary: Investing.com -- Bernstein analysts say the market has overreacted to President Trump’s latest executive order on drug pricing, arguing that the directive poses limited new risks to pharmacy benefit managers (PBMs) despite a sharp selloff in the sector.
